+  fromObservable,
+  fromCallback,
+  fromEventObservable,
+  fromTransition,
+
+  // guard functions
+  stateIn,
+  not,
+  and,
+  or
+}
+```
+
+The `send` action was removed from exports; use `sendTo(...)` or `raise(...)` instead.
